cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper is about deep reinforcement learning algorithms and their performance in a specific environment. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the effects of different algorithmic details on performance, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
